Make it executable:

bash
chmod +x MergTrim
Install it system-wide:

bash
sudo mv MergTrim /usr/local/bin/
sudo sed -i 's/\r$//' /usr/local/bin/MergTrim
Command to excute:
##Replace data with the actual data folder name
MergTrim run-pipeline --input ./data --output ./results

OR 

# First merging
Merge_Trim merge --input ./data --output ./results

# Then trimming  
Merge_Trim trim --input ./data --output ./results